{"tid":1379151,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［推上熱門］推翻暴政就係需要不斷地進化","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:49:34.000Z","uid":146865,"like":168,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"a3bb2821fca37e1c74d4e8c40c18ff8f063f1e64","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"我作為前線手足有幾樣嘢想檢討下<br />\n第一<br />\n最前排一定要有豬嘴同眼罩（眼罩要密封唔好比煙入到去），因為裝備真係好重要，冇豬嘴同眼罩根本狠冇可能頂到啲催淚彈，一射完催淚彈同出速龍就勁混亂，加上啲裝備唔夠嘅手足煙入眼同鼻，令佢哋打唔開眼甚至行唔到，搞到人踩人，所以冇裝備唔好上前線，咁樣只會拖累到啲手足，最後搞到手足比人拉曬，<br />\n第二<br />\n我覺得勇武手足要進化，因為咁多次嘅經驗同我講只守唔攻唔係辦法，好多時set曬防線，都淨係喺原地度等，比曬啲時間狗增援，所以我建議可以喺我哋人多嘅時候亦佢哋人手不足嘅時候攻上去，用人海戰術，前排一定要有盾陣用嚟擋橡膠子彈、海綿彈，我哋有人多嘅優勢，一定可以打殘戰啲狗同搶佢哋啲gear，不過呢一點要有大量勇武手足同齊裝先做得到。<br />\n第三<br />\n我哋可以set一啲陷阱比啲狗，例如攞水喉射濕塊地、撤退嘅時候掉波子，咁樣拎啲狗唔會咁快就衝到過嚟，咁樣可以保障到前線嘅手足，而且set鐵馬同擺雜物嗰阻擋效果唔係太理想（set嘅時間好長）。<br />\n呢幾點喺我暫時諗到，希望各位可以補充或者交流下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcb90784b1f2e7cc7d68fa3cbc1969aa9b8acff","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b60a8a860848a649f357875aac16f0f0d6cda1","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:52:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"93f6955abe3613192691d46db7f8a12bfaff9b91","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"81c3ed08f27aaf1ca794a1a36ebf5ab7c42f44d9","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"cdc6a78c6ac333e868fb4e34219f53168cde4633","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"04991b1e96965df24307bb6a3e2c5dbfc8224f0d","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"35d8c0c1a491f7f51a98711841cca3624b7729c3","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:54:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d354fc45ed19ab902ffd4de2f49a24cb08202769","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:55:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"924609c0738843b5d47cfcc7caa01d00cb2af526","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:55:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7028279060127c6335498de0a85e88e5e364b6cf","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"5a101ce11ccb831f8b437a41885ed92156eb3f6d","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"5ebb73a19815399865472563b0b6b6f751351fe6","tid":1379151,"uid":276704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f294ab5ee5428059e2e18118b810a167b04f08aa","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:57:50.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9362cae80c217c5ff3e4dee0bc9e41541fc399","tid":1379151,"uid":173326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:59:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">防護裝備用完唔好亂掉，呢啲唔係武器，俾人搜到都唔怕。<br />\n俾人查身份證都驚就唔好學人講抗爭。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">黑警問點解帶防具出街，你就答：<br />\n<strong><ins>而家警察落閘唔出勤，市民戴保護裝備出街好合理！<br />\n警察盡責嘅話，我洗攞咁多重野出街食飯？！<br />\n呢啲係冇攻擊性嘅防護措施，唔通海邊嘅救生圈、船上嘅救生衣都犯法？</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>727有兩個情況嚴重，希望平安無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n728少好多full gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><em>所以話防具好重要，尤其係保命嘅電單車頭盔，工地安全帽唔夠保護性！</em></span><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">電單車頭盔要買snell安全標準嘅，聽講可以擋到時速500公里嘅氣槍</span></ins></strong></span>，詳細睇：<a href=\"https://ultimatemotorcycling.com/2013/04/08/motorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fultimatemotorcycling.com%2F2013%2F04%2F08%2Fmotorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=3303e91d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ultimatemotorcycling.com/2013/04/08/motorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[多圖]純防護裝備：頭盔、盾</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372308</a>"},{"pid":"fd1544fffd0e67bc68c2b6e9fdef09c2f4002883","tid":1379151,"uid":231922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:59:52.000Z","msg":"探討黑狗封港鐵站新策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378926</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1ba3dacf855afd03e4e80aecd63d81dffc112dd6","tid":1379151,"uid":290385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbb9bf36ffee852e90868c23df0ba84ba63af9f4","tid":1379151,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"405bd6daa92f4dd0bd26d8d4deace11d3d9ac73d","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:12:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2500d82beca631d6119d9eb645d6f9495153d860","tid":