 />\n<br />\n次次等人排好晒先打 武裝攻防都唔夠 <br />\n今日幾次起陣一tg就散 咁起黎做乜<br />\n<br />\n另外要搵人睇實後方 佔高地<br />\n今日林直街天橋一失 後面包上黎已經可以捉一半人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者可以考慮 前線點火為號 見火全部一定要撒"},{"pid":"aea9ab8a1c950786642f3fe5b2b88d0f485a548e","tid":1379151,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a86ead513dba18db9d58d6ee6e95dbb99a9354f0","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"027b566385e2bddfda54d4b013b03035007e79ca","tid":1379151,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:57:50.000Z","msg":"想知大家對於 一齊衝上去搶gear點睇<br />\n<br />\n利申 咁暴力既野我梗係唔支持啦 傷人架嘛 好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:03:19.000Z","msg":"我都咁覺得，但係一定要齊裝同多人，如果唔係就死緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:05:10.000Z","msg":"需要確實咁肯定有幾多人肯衝<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a3e107a8f02c598d77c9f72b1b41e2177f0286","tid":1379151,"uid":260903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:05:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n借位一share：<br />\n<br />\n如果聽日林鄭下台...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379383</a>"},{"pid":"55354ef69c3b1f022d1c6535cc3ef526c4c7147f","tid":1379151,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:05:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得最主要既目的係激嬲班condom仔，咁我地就有多D料去做文宣同唱班狗"},{"pid":"b80d641db8209904775e7d3e9e2b0835a987261c","tid":1379151,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e81a23db4b447888e85aa62237ca908883c7cfc","tid":1379151,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"027b566385e2bddfda54d4b013b03035007e79ca","tid":1379151,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:57:50.000Z","msg":"想知大家對於 一齊衝上去搶gear點睇<br />\n<br />\n利申 咁暴力既野我梗係唔支持啦 傷人架嘛 好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c